summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Engineer to incur an indebtedness against the General Fund of The City of Seattle, in the sum of One Hundred Fifty and no/100 Dollars ($150.00), on account of the cost and expense of the improvement of East Seventieth Street et al, by grading, etc., as authorized by Ordinance No. 20408, creating Local Improvement District No. 2003.
